ci ai quali, in presenza dei relativi presupposti, la comunicazione Ã¨ prevista obbligatoriamente da disposizioni comunitarie, norme di legge o regolamento.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">La gestione e la conservazione dei dati personali raccolti dalla Scuola XXX avviene su server ubicati allâinterno della stessa.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Periodo di conservazione dei dati</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I dati di navigazione raccolti automaticamente sono conservati solo il tempo necessario (24 ore) per ricavare le informazioni statistiche anonime sullâuso del sito e per controllarne il corretto funzionamento e sono cancellati immediatamente dopo lâelaborazione. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br>\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Per i tempi di conservazione degli altri dati conferiti volontariamente dallâinteressato si rinvia a specifiche informative redatte dagli Uffici competenti.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Diritti dell\'interessato/a</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lâinteressato/a ha diritto di richiedere al Titolare del trattamento, ai sensi degli artt.15, 16, 17, 18, 19 e 21 del Reg. UE 679/2016: l\'accesso ai propri dati personali ed a tutte le informazioni; la rettifica dei propri dati personali inesatti e lâintegrazione di quelli incompleti; la cancellazione dei propri dati, fatta eccezione per quelli contenuti in atti che devono essere obbligatoriamente conservati dalla Scuola XXX e salvo che sussista un motivo legittimo prevalente per procedere al trattamento; la limitazione del trattamento ove ricorra una delle ipotesi di cui allâart.18 del suddetto Regolamento.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lâinteressato/a ha altresÃ¬ il diritto di opporsi al trattamento dei propri dati personali, fermo quanto previsto con riguardo alla necessitÃ  ed obbligatorietÃ  del trattamento ai fini dellâinstaurazione del rapporto; di revocare il consenso eventualmente prestato per i trattamenti non obbligatori dei dati, senza con ciÃ² pregiudicare la liceitÃ  del trattamento basata sul consenso prestato prima della revoca.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lâinteressato/aÂ  potrÃ  esercitare tutti i diritti di cui sopra inviando una e-mail al titolare del trattamento, ovvero allâindirizzo </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">privacy@sns.it</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lâinteressato/a ha altresÃ¬ diritto anche di proporre reclamo allâAutoritÃ  Garante per la Protezione dei dati personali ai sensi dellâart.77 del Reg. UE 679/2016.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Per ogni eventuale chiarimento, il Responsabile della protezione dei dati puÃ² essere contattato allâindirizzo email: </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">dpo@sns.it</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>ObbligatorietÃ  o meno del conferimento dei dati</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salvo quanto specificato per i dati di navigazione, lâutente Ã¨ libero di fornire o meno i propri dati personali. Il conferimento di tali dati puÃ² essere necessario per poter usufruire di alcuni servizi online.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cookies\"><strong>Cookies</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">I cookie sono file di testo che vengono depositati sui computer degli utenti web per consentire lâesplorazione sicura ed efficiente del sito e monitorarne lâutilizzo.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Si informa che nessun dato personale viene acquisito di proposito dal sito.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Questo sito utilizza cookie tecnici necessari per il suo funzionamento e per migliorare lâesperienza dâuso dei propri visitatori</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Questo sito utilizza cookie di profilazione gestiti dalla piattaforma centralizzata </span><a href=\"https://webanalytics.italia.it/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Web Analytics Italia (WAI)</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> di AgID. WAI ospita i dati statistici dei siti web delle PA italiane aderenti al progetto </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;in forma anonima (attraverso il mascheramento di porzioni dellâindirizzo IP dellâutente), informazioni statistiche e aggregate sulle modalitÃ  di navigazione degli utenti (ad es., numero di pagine visitate e accessi, tempo di permanenza nel sito).&nbsp;</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tali cookie sono assimilati ai cookie tecnici e non necessitano del tuo consenso. Inoltre, i predetti cookie analitici, una volta memorizzati sul tuo browser, possono permanere fino a un massimo di 13 mesi, ferma la possibilitÃ  di decidere di disabilitarne lâutilizzo sul proprio browser, in qualsiasi momento, nelle modalitÃ  indicate nel paragrafo che segue.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Per accedere ai contenuti video ospitati direttamente allâinterno del sito, prima della loro visualizzazione ti sarÃ  richiesto di approvare i cookie di profilazione di terza parte di YouTube (</span><a href=\"https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=it\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=it</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">) che attivano anche gli altri identificatori tecnici utilizzati da YouTube per consentirti lo streaming video dal sito. Tali cookie saranno memorizzati sul browser solo dopo aver acquisito il tuo consenso che potrÃ  essere limitato ad un solo video oppure esteso a tutti i video del sito, inserendo la spunta alla voce â</span><b>Ricorda per tutti i video</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">â. Ti ricordiamo che potrai sempre modificare la tua scelta tramite il pulsante â</span><b>Revoca</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">â presente nel paragrafo â</span><b>Gestione cookie</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">â in fondo a questa informativa. La funzionalitÃ  di gestione dei cookie Ã¨ raggiungibile anche dal piede del sito.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Come disabilitare i cookie (opt-out) sul proprio dispositivo</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">La maggior parte dei browser accetta i cookie automaticamente, ma Ã¨ possibile rifiutarli. Se non si desidera ricevere o memorizzare i cookie, si possono modificare le impostazioni di sicurezza del browser utilizzato, secondo le istruzioni rese disponibili dai relativi fornitori ai link di seguito indicati. Nel caso in cui si disabilitino tutti i cookie, il sito potrebbe non funzionare correttamente.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chrome</span></a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://support.mozilla.org/it/kb/protezione-antitracciamento-avanzata-firefox-desktop\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Firefox</span></a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/it-it/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Safari</span></a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://support.microsoft.com/it-it/microsoft-edge/eliminare-i-cookie-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Edge</span></a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><a href=\"https://help.opera.com/en/latest/web-preferences/#cookies\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Opera</span></a></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Privacy policy',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'226-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2025-01-22 15:20:43',	'2025-01-22 14:20:43',	'',	226,	'http://localhost/?p=234',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(236,	1,	'2025-01-22 15:22:17',	'2025-01-22 14:22:17',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This information notice is provided, pursuant to EU Regulation 2016/679 of the European Parliament and Council of April 27, 2016, exclusively for the institutional websites of the Scuola XXX.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Data Controller</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The <strong>Scuola XXX</strong>, represented by its acting Director, located in XXX, P.za Roma 10, phone XXX, certified email: XXX</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, is the data controller for personal data voluntarily provided or automatically collected from the institutional websites.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Data Protection Officer</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Contact details of the Data Protection Officer</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br>XXX</span><a href=\"mailto:dpo@sns.it\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">phone: XXX</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Purpose and Legal Basis of Data Processing</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The personal data described in this notice are processed by the Controller in the performance of its public interest tasks or otherwise connected to the exercise of its public powers, including the task of promoting awareness of the initiatives of the Department for Digital Transformation (Art. 6, Para. 1, Letter e of the GDPR).</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Types of Data Processed, Processing Purposes, and Retention Period</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In compliance with the principles of lawfulness, fairness, transparency, adequacy, relevance, and necessity under Art. 5, Para. 1, of EU Reg. 679/2016, the Data Controller will process personal data automatically collected while browsing the Scuola\'s websites or voluntarily provided for the following purposes:</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Browsing data</span><b>,</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> such as IP addresses, domain names of usersâ computers connecting to the site, URI (Uniform Resource Identifier) addresses of requested resources, request time, method used to submit the request to the server, file size received in response, server response status code (success, error), and other parameters related to the user\'s operating system and IT environment, are collected solely to obtain anonymous statistical information on website use and ensure its proper functioning. Although not collected for the purpose of identifying users, these data could allow user identification through processing and association with data held by third parties. Finally, these data may be used to ascertain liability in the event of potential cybercrimes against the websites.</span></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Data voluntarily provided by users</span><b>,</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> including information, personal, and identifying data collected to enable user access to specific requested services, such as non-institutional email addresses, personal phone numbers, and any special or judicial data voluntarily provided by users during online service usage or by sending requests to published email addresses, are processed solely for institutional purposes and in the interest of the requesting user.</span></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The processing activities and retention periods for the data vary depending on each online service and are detailed in specific notices available on subscription pages.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Categories of Data Recipients and Possible Data Transfers</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The data processed for the above purposes will be communicated or made accessible to employees and collaborators assigned to the relevant offices of the Data Controller, who, as data protection contacts and/or system administrators and/or processing delegates, will be adequately trained by the Data Controller.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Scuola XXX may also communicate personal data to other public administrations if they need to process the data for procedures within their institutional competence, as well as to any public entities to whom communication is mandatory under EU regulations, laws, or regulations.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The management and storage of personal data collected by the Scuola XXX occur on servers located within its premises.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Data Retention Period</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Browsing data automatically collected are retained only for the time necessary (24 hours) to derive anonymous statistical information on website usage and ensure its proper functioning, after which they are immediately deleted. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br>\n</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For the retention periods of other data voluntarily provided by users, please refer to the specific notices prepared by the relevant Offices.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rights of the Data Subject</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The data subject has the right to request from the Data Controller, pursuant to Articles 15, 16, 17, 18, 19, and 21 of EU Reg. 679/2016: access to their personal data and all related information; correction of inaccurate personal data and completion of incomplete data; deletion of personal data, except for those contained in records that must be retained by the Scuola XXX, and unless there is an overriding legitimate reason to process them; restriction of processing in cases specified under Art. 18 of the Regulation.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The data subject also has the right to object to the processing of their personal data, subject to the necessity and obligation of processing for the establishment of a relationship; to withdraw consent, if provided, for non-mandatory data processing, without affecting the lawfulness of processing based on consent before its withdrawal.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The data subject may exercise all the above rights by sending an email to the Data Controller at </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">privacy@sns.it</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br><br></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The data subject also has the right to lodge a complaint with the Data Protection Authority pursuant to Art. 77 of EU Reg. 679/2016.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For any clarification, the Data Protection Officer can be contacted at: </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">dpo@sns.it</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Mandatory or Optional Data Provision</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Except as specified for browsing data, users are free to provide their personal data or not. Providing such data may be necessary to use certain online services.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cookies\"><strong>Cookies</strong></h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cookies are text files stored on users\' computers to enable secure and efficient browsing of the site and monitor its usage.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">No personal data is intentionally acquired by the site.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This site uses technical cookies necessary for its operation and to enhance the user experience.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This site uses profiling cookies managed by the centralized platform </span><a href=\"https://webanalytics.italia.it/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Web Analytics Italia (WAI)</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> by AgID. WAI stores statistical data of Italian public administration websites in an anonymous form (through IP address masking), aggregated statistical information on user navigation (e.g., number of pages visited and accesses, time spent on the site).&nbsp;</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These cookies are assimilated to technical cookies and do not require your consent. Furthermore, these analytical cookies, once stored on your browser, may remain for up to 13 months, subject to the possibility of disabling them at any time via your browser settings as described in the following section.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To access video content hosted directly on the site, before viewing, you will be asked to approve third-party profiling cookies from YouTube (</span><a href=\"https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://policies.google.com/privacy?hl=en</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">) which also activate other technical identifiers used by YouTube to enable video streaming from the site. These cookies will only be stored in your browser after obtaining your consent, which can be limited to a single video or extended to all videos on the site by selecting â</span><b>Remember for all videos</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.â You can always change your choice using the â</span><b>Revoke</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">â button in the â</span><b>Cookie Management</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">â section at the bottom of this notice. The cookie management functionality is also accessible from the site footer.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How to disable cookies (opt-out) on your device</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Most browsers automatically accept cookies, but they can be declined. If you do not wish to receive or store cookies, you can modify your browser\'s security settings according to the instructions provided by the respective providers at the links below. Disabling all cookies may prevent the site from functioning properly.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<l